{
  "stem": "20035.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No explanation, with the exception of, once again, coming back to the famous world of rumor.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's strictly rumors.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's say so.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was really no explanation.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was no such a thing as an official coming over, Hungarian or German military officer would say that you are going x place or doing x, or nothing.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I mean, just like cattle, like sheep, we're-- we're pushed into that car on the guards, of SS guards with machine guns.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there was no such a thing as you disobey or you do anything.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because they had ruthlessly, right in front of us, anybody who tried to disobey, they were just killed.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Gunned down.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So basically, the only knowledge, the only rumor what we had, once again, we are going to go work somehow, somewhere, for the army.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Some kind of labor camp, somewhere where they are going to use us as-- as the slave labor.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And as soon as the door closed, and as soon as the-- the train started to move, just by knowing the country's geography, we knew that we are heading towards the Northeast.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We're heading north and mostly east.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it became quite obvious that we are going towards the Russian front.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We are going towards the Russian-- where basically, the only place for the Hungarian army was there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- and-- and it was, to a certain extent, like a-- not a relief.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But at-- but-- but at least we know where, what we are doing.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That was the rumor.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Then suddenly, we saw that the train is out of Hungary.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Now we are in Poland.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
